reviews.review_text: The 2nd SET THIS IS A GRATEFUL RECORDING !!!!!!

Bummer This is one of those shows, that they should not have pulled from the downloads. Yes it is a soundboard recording....but then again all the audience recordings were soundboard that night. a 24 cable patch was thrown out to the audience, and everybody went wild. I understand the whole pulling of the soundboards, but seriously if they going to let the audience record from a soundboard patch, then they shouldn't pull it. too bad, AWESOME show.
